Reading for Discussion (pick one):
1. A Pragmatic Vision for Interpretability (Nanda et al., 2025) ~15 min
   https://www.alignmentforum.org/posts/StENzDcD3kpfGJssR/a-pragmatic-vision-for-interpretability

2. Against Almost Every Theory of Impact of Interpretability (Segerie, 2023) ~20 min
   https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/LNA8mubrByG7SFacm/against-almost-every-theory-of-impact-of-interpretability-1

3. The Misguided Quest for Mechanistic AI Interpretability (Hendrycks, 2025) ~20 min
   https://ai-frontiers.org/articles/the-misguided-quest-for-mechanistic-ai-interpretability

4. Activation Space Interpretability May Be Doomed (Chughtai & Bushnaq, 2025) ~15 min
   https://www.alignmentforum.org/posts/gYfpPbww3wQRaxAFD/activation-space-interpretability-may-be-doomed
